---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 217
  - Title: Qur’ân
    Location: XLV 26
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=The Art of Dying
---
Allâh giveth life to you, then causeth you to die, then gathereth you
unto the Day of Resurrection whereof there is no doubt. But most of
mankind know not.
